{"tid":1695634,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"點解有冇戴口罩可以令大家不斷互屌","createTime":"2019-11-05T17:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T15:03:15.000Z","uid":60423,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5fc4f4405f075a66a8e67ebc3d6da51e4a6ffb5a","tid":1695634,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:50:33.000Z","msg":"小弟寫字好差，寫到日記咁<br />\nTldr: 戴口罩都只係其中一個活動，無人戴咪代接無人支持/文宣唔夠，點解成日有人講到香港人口罩都唔敢戴所以贏唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />明明其他活動唔多人支持都唔會有參加嘅人屌唔參加嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿唔好屌住先我一開始都有戴但過幾日人少見有狗亂逗戴口罩嘅就廢是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我驚嘅唔係白色恐怖俾佢拉，而係驚自己on9到因為戴口罩而俾佢拉，我寧願做吓港豬留住個人打狗打到俾人拉<br />\n<br />\n但最近俾啲fd屌鳩我做乜唔戴，話鳩我偽黃好惡心，我好無奈但我唔想同佢講我做過咩，都唔應該同任何人講<br />\n我自問由69開始已經參與，我咩都無做過哂，我絕對對得住自己對得住所以香港人，如果你問我應該點回應反蒙面法，我會話蒙住面咁出黎反抗，而唔係戴口罩咁過你平常嘅嘅日子<br />\n當然，兄弟爬山，我絕對同意依個活動，但點解依家變左有戴口罩就等於可以周圍屌鳩人唔付出，唔止連登連日常都有依啲人，咩連口罩都&ldquo;唔敢&rdquo;戴仲想叫人出嚟反抗？仲要拉埋烏克蘭嚟講「人地反蒙面法就即刻蒙面」，咁人地可以咁勇武你又你咪得先<br />\n平時勇武唔可以講自己做乜，就等於無做野？<br />\n點解一個戴口罩活動，就可以拎高地屌人？明明其他活動我唔見有人屌得咁勁<br />\n大家有冇諗過係個活動本身無乜用呢，200萬人戴完又點呢，係咪唔戴口罩就無能力做其他野呢，戴口罩點解要變成所謂基本野呢<br />\n我今日俾人屌到灰，係到夜晚同隊友一齊先好似做得返自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bca489bfcffe07183e9080059ce537a63358ff7","tid":1695634,"uid":60423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:51:25.000Z","msg":"Pish返10下無人睇就算當日記"},{"pid":"2b43c7e0a8ede174cef642bc3edff5dc313937a1","tid":1695634,"uid":60423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"寫完出嚟舒服好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9c10a7c8df16896e54dc93a351e73d3d8a42a6e","tid":1695634,"uid":60423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:52:38.000Z","msg":"唔好屌同路人啦"},{"pid":"1913b6f72b8634fb44442c91ff436d568f758a9b","tid":1695634,"uid":296084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"睇完都係覺得帶個口罩好平常<br />\n<br />\n日日帶 試過帶住嚮狗隔離行過咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8bc5bbfee122b552231ff3e9b0130c307adf37","tid":1695634,"uid":60423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:54:18.000Z","msg":"做過咩都唔會同人講架<br />\n你話成日星期六日ig都吃喝玩樂就話姐"},{"pid":"eccac8a3d4fe8ff3ef7fc51ef04034bdfdccb404","tid":1695634,"uid":60423,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1913b6f72b8634fb44442c91ff436d568f758a9b","tid":1695634,"uid":296084,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:53:35.000Z","msg":"睇完都係覺得帶個口罩好平常<br />\n<br />\n日日帶 試過帶住嚮狗隔離行過咪又係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T17:57:38.000Z","msg":"或者咁講，我都覺好平常<br />\n但問題係無成效，點解仲要迫人做<br />\n依個活動有咩特別，唔參與好似變左唔係同路人咁俾人屌"},{"pid":"3fd2025fe070c96973b14dd1fefdffce9faf5622","tid":1695634,"uid":60423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim